title: Shu Qi - True Woman
description:
Much more satisfying, SHU QI: TRUE WOMAN features the same restless look and cutting but scales back the music video artifice a bit in favor of sunny beach sequences and other attractive, well-lit exteriors. The songs (a mix of French and English) accompanying each segment are agreeable and, after PRIVATE, it is a pleasure to be able to view Shu&#039;s angelic face and devilish body free of "artistic enhancement." As with PRIVATE, there are glimpses of full frontal nudity but neither program is as explicit as Shu&#039;s print pictorials.

Enjoy and seed!
